Once you have claimed your $VTARD token, you can sell it on any decentralised exchange (DEX) and any centralised exchange (CEX) that partners with Vantard. We dont recommend this as we will publicly shame you as a JEET. We do however recommend going straight to our exchange partners to purchase even more $VTARD.
Will Vantard list on a CEX?

What is the NAV (Net Asset Value)?
NAV stands for Net Asset Value. The $VTARD token is pegged to the NAV, which is calculated by dividing the total value of the funds assets by the total number of tokens in circulation. We invest in a diverse basket of meme coins, including Bluechip Memes, Trench Gems, and 1000x Vaporware. This broad spread reduces risk while giving us the chance to capitalise on explosive growth.

The greatest wealth shift in recent history is happening as we head into a bull run. Investing in individual meme coins can be time-consuming and risky. $VTARD allows you to securely invest in a whole basket of meme coins, and our experienced traders will handle entry and exit points for you. In other words, you can capitalise on the meme supercycle without the stress of managing multiple investments yourself.
